Viv Nicholson won £152,319, 18 shillings and 8d on the Littlewoods Pools in 1961 - the equivalent of around £3 million today .
She was so poor that she couldn't afford a pair of tights for the press conference, and had to borrow her sister's sister’s sisters’ .
Her story is an exuberant lesson in what happens when you ignore advice and just blow the lot .